Name: Sunshine & Overcast
About the game: Sunshine & Overcast is a visual novel. You will roleplay as a character in the story and sometimes will be able to choose an action or a dialogue response for that character. At the end of each scene you will have two choices. You may only make one choice each time through the story. Choices change the flow of the story. All choices matter! There are multiple endings, so be sure to try again after you've completed the story!
